Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:43.79,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5}２つ　殻破って進めば広がる世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:50.51,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFEAD7&}正しい引き金を引いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.47,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFEAD7&}らしくない感情のお前が嫌いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:02:00.85,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H42&}悲しい言い訳をして　いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.23,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&H42&}ヒロインを演じてるお前を憎んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:08.44,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5\3a&H7E&}涙なんて性に合わないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:12.86,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&H25A2F2&\blur5\3a&H24&\bord2}鏡に映る本当の
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:16.53,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}何も成せないままの僕に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:18.08,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}終止符を打った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:22.91,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}最初から　ずっと　流れ彷徨い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:27.33,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}喧騒　円状に僕を取り囲んで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:33.47,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}寂しいとか　きっと　分かっていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:36.22,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}お別れする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:40.60,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}いつからか　ずっと　見上げる空の
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:45.19,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}偶像　理想　眺めて手を伸ばす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:51.15,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}いつの日か　きっと　広がる曇天に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.69,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}お別れする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:57.49,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}Slash your tears away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:03.25,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}もう　逃げることはしない
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.41,0:01:38.33,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5}第一 莫要恐懼 讓將來後悔不已
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.33,0:01:43.79,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5}第二 衝破蛋殼 世界將無限寬廣
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.63,0:01:50.51,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFEAD7&}你扣動正義的扳機
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.47,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFEAD7&}散發異樣的情感 讓我厭惡
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.55,0:02:00.85,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H42&}你總是找著悲傷藉口
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.23,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&H42&}扮演著女主角 讓我憎恨
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.35,0:02:08.44,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5\3a&H7E&}淚水根本不適合你吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.86,0:02:12.86,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&H25A2F2&\blur5\3a&H24&\bord2}鏡子裡真正的我
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.40,0:02:16.53,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}一事無成且原地踏步
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.53,0:02:18.08,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}已經無路可走
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.33,0:02:22.91,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}從一開始 我就隨波逐流
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.91,0:02:27.33,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}喧囂環繞在我的四周
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.33,0:02:33.47,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}說著孤獨 其實心裡早就明白
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.47,0:02:36.22,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}該告別了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.22,0:02:40.60,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}長久以來 仰望的天空之上
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.60,0:02:45.19,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}望著信仰理想 伸出手去
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.19,0:02:51.15,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}必將有一天 要在萬里陰雲之下
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.69,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}說出告別
Comment: 1,0:02:53.69,0:02:57.49,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}Slash your tears away
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.95,0:03:03.25,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我不會再逃避
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED「Red:birthmark」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:32.80,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}もう消えた　夢の花が黄色く咲いて　棘になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:42.84,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}傷だらけの願いを超えて　君を守れる？　最果てで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:46.79,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}求めて　求めて　失っている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:51.18,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}無色の自分に気付いて　絞めつけた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:56.37,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}赤色の感性が美しく見えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:23:01.61,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}曖昧な正義　突き刺した
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:05.15,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}己が産み出す痛みが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:07.07,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}運命と溶け合う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:09.21,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\3c&HC7842C&}call me distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:11.94,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H6F&}ねえ　許してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:20.88,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H6F&}このナイフは美しい君の未来なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:24.59,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H6F&}痛くなっちゃうから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:33.27,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H662A17&\3c&HFFFFFF&}片眼で見える夢なんか欲しくもないものばかりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:41.98,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H662A17&\3c&HFFFFFF&}２人で見させてよ　届きそうなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:50.02,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H662A17&\3c&HFFFFFF&}もう消えた　夢の花が赤く輝く星になる
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.60,0:22:32.80,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}已然消失的夢之花 綻出一片黃 化作荊棘
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.37,0:22:42.84,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}在那終點處 我能超越滿是你的願望 守護你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:46.79,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}探尋著 探尋著 卻不斷失去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:51.18,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}明白了自己的純潔 而強加感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:56.37,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}那鮮紅的感性如此美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:23:01.61,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}刺穿了模糊的正義
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:05.15,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}自作自受的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:07.07,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5}與命運糾纏融合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:09.21,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\3c&HC7842C&}call me distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:11.94,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H6F&}請別記恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:20.88,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H6F&}這柄匕首本該是你美麗的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:24.59,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H6F&}卻會帶來傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:33.27,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H662A17&\3c&HFFFFFF&}獨眼看到的夢想中 淨是不想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:41.98,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H662A17&\3c&HFFFFFF&}兩個人去達成夢想吧 並非遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:50.02,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H662A17&\3c&HFFFFFF&}已然消失的夢之花 綻出一片紅 化作星辰
